FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776445554
OL,3,CThe extraordinary claims Starmer is
OL,4,Casking the public to believe on
OL,5,CMandelson
OL,7,FMonday will be a "Westland" moment for
OL,8,FStarmer and Badenoch. I am referring
OL,9,Fto the clash in January 1986 over a
OL,10,Fdefence contract scandal between
OL,11,FMargaret Thatcher and Neil Kinnock in
OL,12,Fthe Commons - when some thought
OL,13,FKinnock had the power to bring down
OL,14,FThatcher but flunked it.
OL,16,FMonday's Commons clash between Starmer
OL,17,Fand Badenoch could well determine each
OL,18,Fof their futures.
OL,20,FIt is make or break for Starmer.
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@[O]
